Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.55,0:00:03.08,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kupikir kita harus menambahkan menu baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.76,0:00:10.02,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Setiap ganti musim pasti ngomong gitu, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.94,0:00:13.70,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Apa itu yang kamu pikirkan untuk musim gugur?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:15.32,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Bukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:19.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tentu kita harus memikirkan menu\N yang musim gugur banget,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.04,0:00:20.45,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}tapi bukan itu masalahnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.81,0:00:24.71,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi menu luar biasa yang dapat mewakili kafe kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.10,0:00:28.21,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Yang bisa viral di TV dan sosial media!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.42,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Itulah yang dibutuhkan kafe-kafe terkenal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.85,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Terus siapa yang harus memikirkannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.85,0:00:36.72,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.72,0:00:39.88,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Palingan mau lempar ke Shiragiku-san lagi, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.08,0:00:45.48,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Kalau sudah punya ide,\N pasti sudah dikerjain sejak dulu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.90,0:00:48.97,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Dia memang bodoh, ya?\NOtaknya bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:49.98,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.98,0:00:53.24,Shiragiku,Shiragiku-san,0,0,0,,Anu ... kurasa enggak sebodoh itu, sih ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.24,0:00:54.73,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Aku mau buat sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.73,0:00:55.88,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Jangan, deh ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.29,0:00:59.00,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ya ampun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.00,0:01:00.12,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.10,0:01:04.91,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Kurasa memikirkan menu baru\N adalah ide yang bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.24,0:01:08.17,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Aku juga suka ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.95,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,... melihat keseriusanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.36,0:01:16.55,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,A-Aku juga suka, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.55,0:01:20.54,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Aku merasa kamu dapat diandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.99,0:01:26.24,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Ini cuma lomba menjatuhkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.24,0:01:28.73,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Siapapun pemenangnya, ini cuma permainan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.59,0:01:32.27,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ah, kalian mempermainkanku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.27,0:01:34.24,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku tidak akan ketipu lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.87,0:01:37.13,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Bakalan buntu untuk sementara waktu, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.13,0:01:41.12,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Benar. Dia enggak memercayai kita lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:43.84,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Kalian ada apa, Akane-chan dan Riho-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.25,0:01:48.44,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Aku sudah menembak Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:54.17,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Pokoknya kita harus menambah menu baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.17,0:01:55.69,Utama,Ami/Ouka/Akane/Riho,0,0,0,,Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.76,0:01:59.34,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Selain itu, kamu antusias banget, ya, Hayato-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.92,0:02:02.85,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Enggak nyangka kamu ingin\N membantuku membuat menu baru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.85,0:02:06.14,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku tak terima diolok-olok Ouka seperti itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.98,0:02:09.85,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Selain itu, sebentar lagi kau masuk kuliah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:12.73,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa terus-terusan mengandalkanmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.73,0:02:14.59,Utama,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu enggak perlu khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.59,0:02:16.81,Utama,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Nanti kusediakan menu yang siap masak, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:20.74,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Walau sekarang tak masalah,\Ntapi tak bisa dibiarkan lama-lama, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.25,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Suatu hari nanti kau juga pasti akan keluar dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:32.28,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,A-Apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.28,0:02:34.75,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kenapa kamu mengatakan hal menyedihkan begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.75,0:02:38.01,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kita keluarga selamanya, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.26,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Yah, tapi kau tak bisa kerja paruh waktu di sini terus ....
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.26,0:02:44.39,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Tapi aku bisa tinggal di sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:48.28,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku juga tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:51.65,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Orang tuamu pasti tidak menginginkannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.40,0:02:54.94,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ya sudah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:58.40,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Jika kamu sejudes itu,\Naku enggak mau ngajarin apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:01.74,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Pikirin saja menu barunya sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:08.00,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf! Aku mengaku salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.00,0:03:10.88,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kau boleh di sini selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.88,0:03:12.08,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.07,0:03:16.50,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,"Kopi buatanmu benar-benar nikmat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.08,0:03:21.75,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Aku harap suatu saat nanti bisa meminumnya sambil memandang bintang-bintang."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.26,0:03:24.48,Utama,Bandmate1,0,0,0,,Eh? Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:26.31,Utama,Bandmate2,0,0,0,,Lirik barunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.59,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Aku mengungkapkan perasaanku kepada orang yang kusuka dan itulah jawabannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:31.02,Utama,Bandmates,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:33.84,Utama,Bandmate1,0,0,0,,Kamu suka sama seseorang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.84,0:03:35.86,Utama,Bandmate2,0,0,0,,Jawaban macam apa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.64,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Kurasa dia bukan menolak, tapi hanya menundanya dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.64,0:03:41.61,Utama,Bandmates,0,0,0,,Dia mempermainkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.37,0:03:45.49,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kue tart ubinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.49,0:03:48.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Wah, kesan musim gugurnya dapat,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.04,0:03:50.70,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,bahan-bahannya juga tak terlalu mahal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.47,0:03:56.42,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Tapi waktu berlalu cepat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.76,0:03:59.30,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Enggak nyangka besok sudah bulan September.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.90,0:04:01.36,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kenapa tiba-tiba bilang begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.36,0:04:03.05,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Bukan apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.39,0:04:06.55,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Rupanya musim panas berlalu begitu cepat, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.55,0:04:08.41,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Iya, benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:11.06,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Artinya juga kita memang sibuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:13.13,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Sibuk saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.19,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya ada hal lainnya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.81,0:04:19.57,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Asmara misalnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.76,0:04:28.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ka-Kau sendiri bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.04,0:04:32.28,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Jika kau menanyakan hal itu,\Nberarti kau mengalami sesuatu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.97,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Nenek memang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.97,0:04:39.86,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu memang enggak pandai bohong, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.86,0:04:40.94,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.52,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku sudah tahu, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:47.05,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tahu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.76,0:04:54.17,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku juga menyukai seseorang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.69,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Walau kami sama-sama suka,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:05:00.11,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,aku enggak bisa menjadi kekasihnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.78,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Karena aku tahu pasti akan membuatnya\N sedih suatu saat nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:06.52,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:12.22,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Akulah yang pertama kali jatuh cinta padamu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:16.57,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku ingin kamu tahu itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:22.62,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,A-Apa yang kau katakan tiba-tiba?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.63,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa kau mabuk lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.40,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku serius!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:30.89,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.89,0:05:34.77,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi jika kau mengatakannya tiba-tiba ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:36.52,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Enggak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.30,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Shiragiku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.08,0:05:45.54,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Asalkan ada aroma ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.64,0:05:47.41,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kau memang mabuk, tuh!{\i1}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.11,0:05:48.41,Utama,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(195,1)\fs16\c&H703F39&\fax-0.4\frz25.2\pos(628.491,324)}Tisu Basah Beralkohol
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:50.67,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tisu itu lagi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.66,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kau tidak usah ikut bebersih lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.11,0:05:55.58,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Nah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:06:00.20,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ayo kita gaskan sebelum yang lain pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.20,0:06:01.67,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apanya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.67,0:06:03.82,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Bagaimana menu barunya--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.34,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Bikin nagih!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.82,0:06:08.71,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:15.22,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Gini, ya, kalau kamu terlalu besar kepala,\N aku juga akan muak padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.78,0:06:17.13,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,He-Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.41,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.36,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Ya ampun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.36,0:06:25.98,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia juga bisa mabuk dengan cara seperti itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:27.51,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:33.16,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kalimat mana saja yang dia ucapkan secara sadar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:39.31,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Maaf memintamu menemaniku belanja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.31,0:06:42.25,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa, ini kan untuk menu baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:45.13,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kuserahkan kafenya pada Ouka dan Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:47.69,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Selain itu, aku juga ingin bertanya padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.45,0:06:51.59,Utama,Wagashi Lady,0,0,0,,Untuk promosi musim gugur ....
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.28,0:06:54.09,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Oh, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.09,0:06:55.24,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.24,0:06:58.75,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Oh, hari ini kencan sama Shiragiku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:01.40,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ka-Kami cuma belanja!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:05.52,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Oh ya, kami sedang memikirkan menu baru.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:08.09,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa kalian punya ide bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:14.16,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua menjual makanan yang unik saat Festival Bunga Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.24,Utama,Wagashi Lady,0,0,0,,Ah, itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.24,0:07:19.16,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Nenekmulah yang mengajari kami membuatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:20.62,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Nenekku?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:21.79,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.79,0:07:24.04,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Dia bilang ketimbang pakai bahan-bahan mahal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.40,0:07:29.42,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,kita bisa membuat makanan enak dan unik\Nmemakai ide sederhana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:34.18,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Yah, saran dari koki restoran bintang tiga \Nmemang luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:34.18,Utama,Wagashi Lady,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:37.90,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hah? Apa maksudmu restoran bintang tiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.90,0:07:39.18,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,A-Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.18,0:07:44.41,Utama,Fishman,0,0,0,,Tidak, maksudku dia setara orang sehebat itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.41,0:07:48.57,Utama,Wagashi Lady,0,0,0,,Ya ampun! Makanya jangan ngelantur terus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:50.57,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ayo pergi, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:51.57,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:57.50,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Se-Sebaiknya kita pakai bahan-bahan lokal\N untuk menu baru kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.50,0:08:00.26,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Mumpung kafe kita di tepi pantai ....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.16,0:08:07.09,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, kau tahu sesuatu tentang Nenekku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.09,0:08:11.72,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Eh? Tiba-tiba kamu ngomong apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:13.97,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku ubah pertanyaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.67,0:08:19.02,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan di kamar Nenekku setiap malam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:28.98,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Hei, Ayah, apa tulisannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:31.02,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,"Familia."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.52,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Artinya "keluarga" dalam bahasa Spanyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.11,0:08:39.49,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Di sinilah guru Ayah, Dewi Masak tinggal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.70,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Selamat datang.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:47.36,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Akhirnya aku menemukanmu, Kasukabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.36,0:08:49.34,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Ono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.34,0:08:53.47,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Iya. Terima kasih sudah mengajariku\N saat di restoran Spanyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.97,0:08:57.97,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya aku ingin membuka restoran di Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:09:00.14,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Aku ingin memberitahumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:01.42,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.42,0:09:02.73,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Hei, Ayah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:06.30,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aromanya harum!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.30,0:09:09.31,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Iya, benar. Mungkin aroma kue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.31,0:09:12.80,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Kasukabe-san, dia adalah putriku, Shiragiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.80,0:09:14.19,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Selamat siang.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.90,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Kamu, ya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:21.58,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Aku sangat ingin mengenalkannya kepadamu, Kasukabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.01,0:09:24.92,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah menjadi Ayah, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:27.34,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Iya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.34,0:09:29.08,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Nenek!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.36,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku ingin coba kue yang tadi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.59,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,He-Hei, Shiragiku!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:35.22,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Habisnya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.31,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Maaf, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.31,0:09:40.72,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Setelah agak dingin, nanti nenek berikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:42.91,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Kue keju labunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.91,0:09:45.48,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Wah, kue keju labu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.48,0:09:46.99,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.99,0:09:51.69,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa, itu kan menu baru,\Naku ingin dengar pendapatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.11,0:09:56.70,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh ya, aku membaca menu yang dipajang di luar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:01.39,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Semuanya makanan ringan, seperti kafe-kafe biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:07.85,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Bukankah kemampuanmu sanggup untuk membuka restoran yang lebih mewah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:10.73,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Nenek!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:12.84,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku lapar! Lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:15.26,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:18.00,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hei, sabar sebentar lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.00,0:10:20.47,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Nanti nenek buatkan pilaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:22.44,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Nenek lampir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.22,0:10:27.53,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hayato! Dasar anak nakal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.53,0:10:28.79,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.48,0:10:32.98,Utama,Dad,0,0,0,,Apa anak barusan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:35.60,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Dia cucuku, Hayato.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.60,0:10:39.44,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Mulutnya kasar entah mirip siapa ....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:41.88,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Oh ya, Shiragiku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.79,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Hayato-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.74,0:10:49.25,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Nenek memberikan es krim.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:51.50,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ayo makan bareng?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:57.01,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Hayato-kun pergi ke mana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.68,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Apa dia di luar?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.65,0:11:09.08,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.89,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Apa yang sudah kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.89,0:11:12.96,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Sepatu ini baru saja kubeli!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.96,0:11:15.27,Utama,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ma-Maaf!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:17.69,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Kau kira minta maaf sudah cukup?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.78,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Jangan kira anak kecil bisa diampuni!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.78,0:11:21.86,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Kau kira berapa harga sepatuku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.56,0:11:23.78,Utama,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:27.04,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Katakan sesuatu!\NDi mana orang tuamu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:30.02,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,{\i1}Bagaimana ini?\NTolong aku ....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.78,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Bahaya kalau berdiri di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.55,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku sedang bersih-bersih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.18,0:11:41.60,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Bajingan ....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:43.43,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Sudah kubilang bahaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.43,0:11:45.30,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kau menggangguku!\NPulang sana!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.34,0:11:48.33,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.19,0:11:50.83,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Aku takkan memaafkanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.06,Utama,Woman1,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.06,0:11:54.88,Utama,Woman2,0,0,0,,{\an8}Anak kecil baru menyemprot air kepadanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.88,0:11:57.94,Utama,Woman3,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kekanak-kanakan banget gitu doang langsung marah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.80,Utama,Woman4,0,0,0,,Siapa orang itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:02.20,Utama,Woman5,0,0,0,,Dia Fuwa-san, mantan duta besar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.18,Utama,Woman4,0,0,0,,Ah, dia, toh!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:06.91,Utama,Fuwa,0,0,0,,Awas saja kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.23,0:12:08.50,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.50,0:12:10.22,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,A-Anu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.91,0:12:13.24,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Te-Terima kasih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.79,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku benci orang itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.79,0:12:17.79,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia selalu jahat kepada Nenekku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:23.55,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa pernah terjadi hal seperti itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.64,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku sama sekali tidak ingat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:28.05,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu masih kecil, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:29.98,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kenapa kau tak pernah menceritakannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.98,0:12:32.64,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tak ada salahnya menceritakannya, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.88,0:12:38.94,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Jika aku menceritakannya, nanti kamu tahu kalau nenekmu adalah mantan koki.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.94,0:12:42.16,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Terus kenapa aku tidak boleh tahu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.16,0:12:46.82,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kenalan Nenekku juga sepertinya\N merahasiakannya dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.15,0:12:50.33,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku enggak bisa memberitahumu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.12,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Izinkan aku bekerja di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.21,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ayahku sudah mengizinkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.21,0:12:57.08,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Shiragiku-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:01.46,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku bercita-cita menjadi koki, jadi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.77,0:13:03.92,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ayahku menghormatimu, Kasukabe-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:06.26,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku ingin belajar banyak hal darimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.18,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berjanji kepada Nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:12.10,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Janji?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.31,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.70,0:13:21.32,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Jika tidak keberatan,\N nenek bisa mengajarimu pada saat kafe lengang.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.32,0:13:22.81,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Benarkah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:27.12,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Tapi tolong berjanji satu hal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.93,0:13:30.81,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Alasan nenek berhenti menjadi koki ....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:34.85,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Jika suatu saat nanti kamu bertemu Hayato,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:37.29,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,bisa tolong rahasiakan alasan itu darinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.96,0:13:42.41,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Berarti kau bisa menceritakan hal selain\N dari perjanjian itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:51.60,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa setiap malam kau mencari foto-foto semasa Nenekku memasak di Spanyol?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:57.73,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Nenek menyembunyikannya supaya Hayato tidak tahu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.14,0:14:01.30,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,tapi sebaiknya nenek buang saja, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.73,0:14:04.91,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.62,0:14:08.36,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku sudah mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.11,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:12.86,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kuyakin Nenek berhenti menjadi koki ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:15.67,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,... gara-gara aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.50,0:14:20.75,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Semuanya! Lihat ini!\NAku sudah mencetaknya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.75,0:14:22.65,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Keren!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.65,0:14:24.50,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Iya, foto yang bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.80,0:14:27.42,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Oh ya, ayo pajang di kafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:29.10,Utama,Riho/Akane/Ami,0,0,0,,Ide bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.88,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Mau di pajang sebelah mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:32.01,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Sebelah sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.38,0:14:34.65,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia pergi ke Spanyol saat usia 43 tahun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:38.17,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Restoran tempat dia menjadi kepala koki \Nselama 15 tahun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.17,0:14:39.87,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,... menjadi restoran bintang tiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.52,0:14:45.90,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kemudian dia berencana membuka\N restoran sendiri bernama Anhelo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.30,0:14:49.02,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tepat sebelum restoranya selesai,\Ndia membatalkan pembangunannya ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.02,0:14:51.08,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,... dan kembali ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:55.16,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Lalu dia merawatku setelah orang tuaku meninggal dalam kecelakaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.53,0:14:57.61,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,dan membuka kafe ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.86,0:15:03.38,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kuyakin Nenek seharusnya bisa membuka restoran setelah pulang ke sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.51,0:15:07.08,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi aku menjadi bebannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.08,0:15:08.92,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Itu enggak benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.92,0:15:12.49,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu enggak membebani Nenekmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:13.68,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Shiragiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.14,0:15:15.93,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu enggak salah--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:17.06,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi memang benar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.44,0:15:20.60,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Seorang koki restoran bintang tiga\N pasti diminati banyak investor.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:24.89,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Tapi supaya restorannya terkenal dan\N menghasilkan untung banyak,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.89,0:15:28.44,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,dia harus membuka restoran \Ndi lokasi ramai di Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:33.26,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Jika Nenek melakukannya, maka aku akan tinggal sendirian di rumah sebesar ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.09,0:15:38.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Anggaplah dia berhutang untuk \Nmembuka restoran di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.48,0:15:41.04,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kemungkinan dia akan terkenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.50,0:15:43.92,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, sudah pasti aku akan mengetahui ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:47.03,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,... alasan Nenek kembali ke kota ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:52.68,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Restoran yang ingin Nenek buka\N di Spanyol bernama "Anhelo",
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.68,0:15:55.51,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,yang artinya adalah "Kedambaan"\N dalam bahasa Spanyol.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.21,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku paham betul sifat Nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.60,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia tidak ingin meninggalkan cucunya sendirian,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.60,0:16:07.45,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,dan dia tidak ingin cucunya tahu bahwa\N dia mengubur impiannya karena cucunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:14.14,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia pun memilih menjadi nenek-nenek biasa \Nwalau harus hidup miskin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.16,0:16:19.12,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Itu alasan Nenekku berhenti menjadi koki, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:20.33,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Tapi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.44,0:16:25.21,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Oh ya, apa kau ...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.21,0:16:28.46,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,... orang yang hanya memacari orang \Nyang yakin kau nikahi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:31.46,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Eh?! Kenapa tiba-tiba bilang begitu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:35.97,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kau pernah bilang tak bisa menjadi kekasihnya walau kalian saling suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:39.10,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dan takut akan membuatnya sedih suatu saat nanti.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.62,0:16:47.61,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Jika kita menikah, aku pasti akan tahu rahasia kalau Ayahmu adalah murid koki Nenekku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.63,0:16:51.36,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku telah merenggut impian Nenekku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:56.81,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku pernah bertanya kepadanya satu kali!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.74,0:17:00.79,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Apakah dia menyesal berhenti menjadi koki atau enggak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.12,0:17:05.75,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Ah? Tidak, sama sekali tidak pernah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.03,0:17:10.75,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Tapi Ayahku bilang memasak \Nadalah motivasi hidup nenek ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.07,0:17:15.96,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya hidup Nenek bersama Hayato-kun ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:20.64,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,... selama 10 tahun sangat bahagia hingga Nenek tak memedulikannya lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.16,0:17:24.07,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Di sana ada coretan gambar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:27.04,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Hayato yang menggambarnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.04,0:17:29.82,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Kursi yang terlihat jelas dari posisi Nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.27,0:17:33.06,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Itu adalah kursi kesukaannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.79,0:17:36.12,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Nenek tak masalah tak punya uang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:42.73,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Melihat pertumbuhan Hayato setiap hari adalah hal paling membahagiakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:46.10,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Dia benar-benar lucu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:52.05,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Jika Nenek punya motivasi hidup sekarang,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.44,0:17:53.82,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,maka ....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.95,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Itu kamu, Hayato-kun!\NKamulah motivasi hidup Nenek!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.54,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Mana mungkin kamu membebaninya!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.17,0:18:07.94,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Dia tidak pernah mengatakannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.90,0:18:13.61,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kamu paham betul sifat Nenekmu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:25.16,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Berapa kali lagi Nenek bisa melihat bunga sakura seperti ini bersamamu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.61,0:18:28.29,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kita bisa melihatnya berkali-kali, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:31.30,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Nenek kan umur panjang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.52,0:18:34.51,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.51,0:18:39.43,Utama,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Nenek takkan meninggal sebelum bisa usil kepada istrimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:40.93,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:42.44,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.32,0:18:51.60,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Iya, kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.60,0:18:55.72,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku mendapat kasih sayang\N tak terbalas dari Nenek di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:19:00.07,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Makanya takkan kubiarkan hancur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:05.70,Shiragiku,Hayato,0,0,0,,Saat Nenek meninggal, aku sudah putuskan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.01,0:19:07.10,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:12.50,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Jika kamu kembali dan ingin meneruskan kafe ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.09,0:19:18.07,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,apapun yang terjadi,\Naku akan mendukungmu sekuat tenaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:22.92,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku akan mendukungmu sebagai keluargamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.27,0:19:27.38,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Begitu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:32.57,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Yah, aku mohon bantuanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:33.45,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.97,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Aku juga akan berjuang keras!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.08,0:19:40.51,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Aku juga!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:41.99,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nenek!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.08,0:19:42.56,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Hei ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.74,0:19:48.12,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi kalian nguping, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.41,0:19:50.11,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Air mataku tak dapat berhenti!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:53.54,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Itu adalah cerita paling epik seumur hidupku!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.22,0:19:55.30,Utama,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Teman-teman ....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.05,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Aku membencimu, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.05,0:20:00.63,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Tapi Nenek ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.09,0:20:03.85,Utama,Five,0,0,0,,Aku menyayanginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.39,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kalian berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.66,0:20:11.93,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Aku pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:16.44,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Apa ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.44,0:20:17.92,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Astaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.07,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Panas-panas begini kau berisik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.12,0:20:22.57,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Aku pulang, Papa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.28,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Jangan panggil aku "Papa."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.28,0:20:27.49,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Panggil aku "Ayah" atau "Hayato-sensei."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:31.62,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Kenapa aku harus manggil orang tuaku "Sensei"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.62,0:20:36.06,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Memang berkat siapa nilai SMP-mu tidak jeblok?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:41.38,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Selain itu, ini foto Mama, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:44.01,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Iya. Kau bisa tahu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.64,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Habisnya mirip banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.64,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Wah, muda banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:51.98,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Ah, apa keempat cewek lainnya ....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.98,0:20:55.35,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Aku menemukan foto ini saat bebersih ruangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.35,0:20:57.48,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Biar aku simpan lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.69,0:21:00.24,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:03.44,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Fotonya kan bagus!\NMending dipajang!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.48,0:21:05.45,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Hei ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.45,0:21:09.28,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Pada masa-masa ini,\N Mama cuma karyawan paruh waktu, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:10.09,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.59,0:21:13.71,Utama,Daughter,0,0,0,,Berarti sejak kapan mulai menyukai Mama?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.80,0:21:16.96,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Entahlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.96,0:21:19.55,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Sudah terlalu lama, aku lupa.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:27.47,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Kelihatan dari kejauhan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.47,0:21:28.97,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Benar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:31.35,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Iya! Ombaknya tinggi-tinggi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:34.73,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Kenapa malah pergi piknik pas hari libur?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:38.04,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Hayacchi! Aku lapar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.40,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Nah, Hayato-kun!\NGelar tikarnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.40,0:21:41.48,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Iya, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:44.11,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Kelihatan enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.11,0:21:46.44,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Selamat makan!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.68,0:21:49.80,Ami,Ami,0,0,0,,Enak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:51.39,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, Shiragiku-san ....
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.39,0:21:52.24,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.70,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Apa yang kamu maksud saat itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:57.37,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Katanya kamu harus menikahi setiap\N yang menjadi pasanganmu,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:00.13,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,atau enggak bisa menikahi pasanganmu\N walau saling suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:03.76,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Ah, itu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:06.26,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,A-Ada apa, Kiku-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.26,0:22:08.03,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Oh ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.03,0:22:11.64,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku enggak perlu ngejaga rahasia\N masa lalu Nenek lagi ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.14,0:22:15.43,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Berarti aku juga bisa menjadi calon pacar Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:21.02,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Lalu jika aku menikahinya suatu hari nanti ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:23.03,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Calon pacarnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.46,0:22:26.53,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Jangan-jangan kamu sama Hayato-kun ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:31.53,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Kamu bilang "Aku juga",\Nartinya ada orang lain ...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.53,0:22:33.62,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,... yang menyukai Hayato-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.79,0:22:37.41,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,A-Anu, bukan begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:39.45,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Aku enggak begitu ....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.51,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Kiku-chan! Itu gelasku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.67,0:22:46.68,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Itu wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.68,0:22:48.39,Utama,Hayato/Ami/Ouka/Akane,0,0,0,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:50.55,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Meong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.89,0:22:52.93,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Meong, meong, meong!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.24,0:22:57.31,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Benar! Aku menyukai Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.31,0:22:58.68,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:00.40,Akane,Akane,0,0,0,,Merepotkan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.40,0:23:02.69,Riho,Riho,0,0,0,,Sejak kapan dia mabuk, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.15,0:23:05.68,Ouka,Ouka,0,0,0,,Kita lagi di luar!\NBuruan hentikan dia!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:09.99,Shiragiku,Shiragiku,0,0,0,,Setelah membuat makanan,\Nberikutnya membuat anak, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.99,0:23:11.07,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Apa kau bodoh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.04,0:23:14.75,Utama,Riho/Akane/Ouka,0,0,0,,Jangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.75,0:23:17.53,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:20.00,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\i1}Di suatu kafe tua tepi pantai ...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.00,0:23:22.33,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\i1}... katanya ada dewi di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.23,0:23:27.63,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\i1}Apakah mereka adalah \Ndewi keberuntungan penyelamat kafe ini,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.30,Utama,Hayato,0,0,0,,{\i1}atau jin kemiskinan yang akan menghancurkan kafe?
